\[K_{1}R^{*}_{11}+K_{2}R^{*}_{12}\] \[=s^{\prime}(i)d(g)\frac{\theta}{\sin\theta}\big{[}\cos\big{(}s(i) -1\big{)}\theta\cos\big{(}2s(i)-1\big{)}\theta+\sin\big{(}s(i)-1\big{)}\theta \sin\big{(}2s(i)-1\big{)}\theta\big{]}\] \[=s^{\prime}(i)d(g)\frac{\theta}{\sin\theta}\cos s(i)\theta.\]

Следовательно,\[R_{1}=s(i)\bigg{(}\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\bigg{)}^{2}+s(i)\frac{ \sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}s^{\prime}(i)d(g)\frac{\theta}{\sin\theta}\cos s(i)\theta. \tag{4.26}\]

_Расчет \(R_{2}\)_. Пусть

\[R^{*}_{21}=\bigg{(}\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\bigg{)}^{2}\frac{ \partial s(i)}{\partial\theta},\]\[R_{22}^{*} =\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\left\{\frac{dx_{1}(i)}{d\theta} \biggl{[}-K_{2}\frac{\partial s(i)}{\partial x_{2}}-K_{1}\frac{\partial s(i)}{ \partial x_{1}}\biggr{]}-\frac{dx_{2}(i)}{d\theta}\biggl{[}K_{1}\frac{\partial s (i)}{\partial x_{2}}-K_{2}\frac{\partial s(i)}{\partial x_{1}}\biggr{]}\right\}\] \[=\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\left\{K_{2}\biggl{[}\frac{dx_{2 }(i)}{d\theta}\frac{\partial s(i)}{\partial x_{1}}-\frac{dx_{1}(i)}{d\theta} \frac{\partial s(i)}{\partial x_{2}}\biggr{]}-K_{1}\biggl{[}\frac{dx_{1}(i)}{d \theta}\frac{\partial s(i)}{\partial x_{1}}+\frac{dx_{2}(i)}{d\theta}\frac{ \partial s(i)}{\partial x_{2}}\biggr{]}\right\}.\]

Разлагаем по третьей колонке \(R_{2}^{*}\) и получаем, что \(R_{2}^{*}=R_{21}^{*}+R_{22}^{*}\), следовательно, \(R_{2}=\theta\,R_{21}^{*}+\theta\,R_{22}^{*}\).

Помня, что \(d(g)=\frac{\theta}{\sin\theta}\|x\|\), получаем

\[\frac{\partial s(i)}{\partial\theta}=s^{\prime}(i)\frac{\partial d(g)}{ \partial\theta}=s^{\prime}(i)\frac{\sin\theta-\theta\cos\theta}{\sin^{2}\theta} \|x\|=s^{\prime}(i)d(g)\frac{1}{\theta}\frac{\sin\theta-\theta\cos\theta}{\sin \theta},\]

следовательно,

\[R_{21}^{*}=\biggl{(}\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\biggr{)}^{2}s^{\prime}( i)d(g)\frac{1}{\theta}\frac{\sin\theta-\theta\cos\theta}{\sin\theta}.\]

Чтобы рассчитать \(R_{22}^{*}\), нам потребуется явное выражение \(\frac{dx_{1}(i)}{d\theta}\) и \(\frac{dx_{2}(i)}{d\theta}\). Обозначим'\[U_{1}=\frac{d}{d\theta}\frac{\sin\theta+\sin(2s(i)-1)\theta}{2 \sin\theta}=\frac{2s(i)\sin\theta\cos(2s(i)-1)\theta-\sin 2s(i)\theta}{2 \sin^{2}\theta},\] \[U_{2}=\frac{d}{d\theta}\frac{\cos\theta-\cos(2s(i)-1)\theta}{2 \sin\theta}=\frac{-1+2s(i)\sin\theta\sin(2s(i)-1)\theta+\cos 2s(i)\theta}{2 \sin^{2}\theta}.\]

Тогда, по (4.22) и (4.23),

\[\frac{dx_{1}(i)}{d\theta}=x_{1}U_{1}+x_{2}U_{2},\qquad\frac{dx_{2}(i)}{d\theta }=-x_{1}U_{2}+x_{2}U_{1}.\]

Используя (4.20) и (4.21), мы находим, что

\[R_{22}^{*} =\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}s^{\prime}(i)\frac{1}{d(g)} \biggl{(}\frac{\theta}{\sin\theta}\biggr{)}^{2}\|x\|^{2}(-K_{2}U_{2}-K_{1}U_{1})\] \[=-\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}s^{\prime}(i)d(g)(K_{1}U_{1} +K_{2}U_{2})\quad\text{поstackoverflow (\ref{eq:R22})}\] \[=-\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}s^{\prime}(i)d(g)\frac{s(i) \sin\theta\cos s(i)\theta-\cos\theta\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin^{2}\theta},\]

где мы трижды использовали элементарные формулы, связывающие тригонометрические функции в последней равенстве.

因此, мы имеем

\[R_{2}=\theta\,R_{21}^{*}+\theta\,R_{22}^{*}=s^{\prime}(i)d(g)\left\{\left( \frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\right)^{2}-\theta\,\frac{\sin s(i)\theta}{ \sin\theta}\frac{s(i)\cos s(i)\theta}{\sin\theta}\right\}. \tag{4.27}\]

По (4.18), (4.26) и (4.27), мы получаем (4.17).

